Clone the repository to your local machine:
Open the project in your favorite Java IDE.
Run the App class, which contains the main method.
The Hangman game window should appear. Enter a letter in the provided text field and press Enter to make a guess.
The game will display the progress, the letters guessed, and the remaining guesses. If the game ends, a message will indicate whether you won or lost.

How to Play
Guess letters by entering them in the text field and pressing Enter.
The game allows uppercase and lowercase letters.
The "Start New Game" button resets the game for a new round.

